FT  19 DEC 94 / Company News (This Week and Next): Eurotherm - Other
companies
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The industrial process control equipment supplier has performed well in
recent years by cutting costs and improving productivity. Now investors are
looking for evidence that the management under Mr Claes Hultman, chief
