Pounds 200,000 annually
Secretary: Maj. Michael Hankinson
Chairman: Peter Lee
Peter Lee
Deputy chairman Leeds based Carclo Engineering Group, great grandson of
founder of Sheffield steel maker Arthur Lee &amp; Sons, grand name in UK
metals industry which was bought by Carclo this summer. Low-key
fundraiser
