FT  17 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: Drug network smashed
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An investigation by the US Drug Enforcement Administration cracked a
money-laundering network and found links between the Mafia and Colombia's
Cali cartel. The probe led to the seizure of nine tons of cocaine and
Dollars 52m (Pounds 33m) in cash, and the arrest of 88 people.
