FT  17 DEC 94 / UK Company News: Moorgate assets dip
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Moorgate Investment Trust saw undiluted net asset value per share dip by 5.3
per cent, from 162.1p to 153.5p, during the half year to November 30 - a
modest outperformance against its benchmark, the Hoare Govett Smaller
Companies Index, which fell 6.2 per cent over the same period.
